data.description: Now offering $2500 towards buyers closing cost. Contact your agent for details. Gorgeous home in the Moss Bluff Subdivision in North Lafayette. This immaculate home is a three bedroom, 2 full bath, 1689 sqft with 10 ft ceilings and an open floor plan.  Just walking into the front door, you will notice the neutral colors and amazing ceramic tile.  With granite counter tops and upgraded backsplash, you will be amazed.  The huge closets and awesome master suite is sure to please anyone. Do not hesitate on viewing this home. It will not last long. Schedule your viewing today.
